{"tid":671721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[英國皇室] 梅根擁美國籍...恐被查稅","createTime":"2018-05-20T11:13:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-20T22:44:14.000Z","uid":141151,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"36c3c42a5a7b8fc68abc1dcd8e8147b55a289a80","tid":671721,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T11:13:35.000Z","msg":"梅根擁美國籍...恐被查稅<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://money.udn.com/money/story/5599/3151781\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F5599%2F3151781&d=oKrDNViBTcHj%2FpYdazgxp8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=fb28dd66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://money.udn.com/money/story/5599/3151781</a><br />\n<br />\n英國哈利王子19日和美國女星梅根馬克爾完婚，只是沒有想到梅根一嫁入皇家，便讓英國王室碰到可能得向美國政府報稅的麻煩。<br />\n<br />\n梅根嫁入皇室，想必會申請取得英國國籍，同時也必須放棄美籍，但是其中的手續相當複雜，可能至少得花上五年，才能走完全部程序。<br />\n<br />\n而且只要她仍然保有美國國籍，就算是長居國外，凡是她名下的資產和所得，都必須要向美國的國稅局申報。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國國稅局規定，凡所得30萬美元以上者，必須詳列申報海外資產。這也就是說，只要梅根拿了英國王室的錢，都必須申報給美國國稅局。<br />\n<br />\n如此一來，梅根夫家的資產也可能因此跟著曝光，這必定讓英國王室十分為難，因為長期以來，英國王室從來沒有對外透露本身的財務狀況。<br />\n<br />\n此外，倘若梅根和哈利王子成立聯名帳戶，哈利本人的財務狀況也將落入美國國稅局的掌握。<br />\n<br />\n哈利王子據說擁有已故母親黛安娜王妃留下資產轉投資的收入，也從父親查理王子那裡拿到津貼。<br />\n<br />\n因此，稅務專家猜測，兩人很可能不會設立合併帳戶。<br />\n<br />\n不過梅根本人其實也身價不菲，靠著多年來的演戲以及廣告代言收入，財產淨值約在390萬英鎊（525萬美元）。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，考量到英國王室擁有淨值至少數十億計美元的資產，面對如此難題，肯定會雇請最有經驗的財務顧問團隊，提供新任王妃梅根最好的建議。"},{"pid":"3c3302a7b0819bb3ef4a15cebde020928b9ce883","tid":671721,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T11:16:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de6175519a4dee2c72113c26e951537c14d1f650","tid":671721,"uid":41245,"like":7,"dislike":18,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T11:16:59.000Z","msg":"5百幾萬美金嘅星係身價不菲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n噉依個世界冇窮人啦<br />\n台狗真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17999e39c070fba25f558c08be32d326afb1dfa4","tid":671721,"uid":126283,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T11:25:10.000Z","msg":"講到英國王室好似冇考慮過呢點咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過咁，如果要收稅都幾得意，前殖民地收番宗主錢"},{"pid":"14d8b5a2328cef51ab6c59415e5f5c4a9f6e59ba","tid":671721,"uid":115484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T11:26:40.000Z","msg":"She will need to stay in the UK for at lease 5 years before getting British Citizenship."},{"pid":"f21210ebc6d9abe597af0ba09973a5123f74b57f","tid":671721,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"17999e39c070fba25f558c08be32d326afb1dfa4","tid":671721,"uid":126283,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T11:25:10.000Z","msg":"講到英國王室好似冇考慮過呢點咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過咁，如果要收稅都幾得意，前殖民地收番宗主錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T11:29:08.000Z","msg":"噉美國咪冇英資？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79c9c9e2c1fa9cf8a85eb1288e1d21a98e355595","tid":671721,"uid":126283,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f21210ebc6d9abe597af0ba09973a5123f74b57f","tid":671721,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"17999e39c070fba25f558c08be32d326afb1dfa4","tid":671721,"uid":126283,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T11:25:10.000Z","msg":"講到英國王室好似冇考慮過呢點咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過咁，如果要收稅都幾得意，前殖民地收番宗主錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T11:29:08.000Z","msg":"噉美國咪冇英資？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T11:30:29.000Z","msg":"我指英國王室"},{"